    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I run into the same trouble because I want my food to be very easy .. no fool proof. I&#8217;m not a great cook, but so often what I make tastes like nothing. The salad sounds delicious though. See&#8230; redeemed. 🙂</p>
    </div>

