    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>This is my first time commenting on your lovely blog. </>I am not a chef, (my husband is a fabulous cook) but I am definitely a foodie. When I get a bee in my bonnet and decide to venture into the kitchen, I want to make something yummy and EASY. So thank you for the inspiration for this fantastic salad. I changed it a little&#8230;only because I didn&#8217;t have a white vinegar so I used lemon juice and made a tangy vinaigrette which worked well with the DELICIOUS pear I used, and I used ricotta salata instead of parmesan, but that&#8217;s only because I love ricotta salata and use it whenever possible. The end result was delicious. My mouth is watering thinking about it, so I guess I&#8217;ll have to make it again tomorrow. 🙂</>Thanks again!!</p>
    </div>

